						               													<description>It's Game Time, Let's Roll! &amp;trade;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Now with GRIDDLE!QuickPlay option: A complete game in just 30 minutes!!!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;American Football meets Backgammon! &amp;trade;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;GRIDDLE! is an intriguing, fast-paced, 2-player game for anyone who enjoys Backgammon (and other strategically similar games), where you weigh the odds, as well as your opponent's style of play, when deciding how to execute each roll of the dice.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Throw in a unique time management system, along with an American Football theme, and you've got a clean, crisp, &amp;quot;non-sports&amp;quot; game of strategy and chance that doesn't bog down in the tediousness of endless chart referencing!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Although no knowledge or terminology of American Football is necessary, the GRIDDLE! experience will satisfy both the &amp;quot;sports&amp;quot; and &amp;quot;non-sports&amp;quot; gamer in everyone!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The Challenge:&amp;#10;Outscore your opponent by balancing offensive and defensive strategy, while managing time and the probabilities presented with every roll of the dice!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The Contents:&amp;#10;1 - GRIDDLE!Stadium Gameboard&amp;#10;8 - Scoreboard Markers&amp;#10;5 - Dual-color Game Pieces (Gridders)&amp;#10;1 - Set of 5 Dice w/ Dots&amp;#10;1 - Set of 5 Dice w/ Digits&amp;#10;1 - Plastic Coin&amp;#10;1 - GRIDDLE!Rules Booklet&amp;#10;     (with GRIDDLE!QuickPlay)&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Players: 2&amp;#10;Ages: 7 to Adult&amp;#10;Playing Time: 1 Hour (1/2 hour using GRIDDLE!QuickPlay option)&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
